{"name": "legacy-font-converter", "metadata": {"name": "legacy-font-converter", "version": "0.1.3", "classifiers": ["License :: OSI Approved :: MIT License", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.10", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.11", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.12", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.13", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.6", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.7", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.8", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.9"], "home_page": "https://github.com/Abdur-Rahim-sheikh/legacy-font-converter", "license": "MIT", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": [], "summary": "A tool to convert between legacy font and unicode", "upload_time": 1735637133}, "documentation": ["# Abdur-Rahim Sheikh Legacy Font Converter\n\nA Python package for converting legacy fonts.\n\n## Introduction\nIn today's context we use or will use LLM (Large Language Models) in our daily life. But the problem is that the LLMs are trained on the Unicode text. But in many cases, we have to deal with the legacy fonts. So, this package will help you to convert the legacy fonts to Unicode text.\n\nSpecially for Bangla language, there are many legacy fonts like SutonnyMJ, SolaimanLipi, etc. Which are used in docx files, pdf files, etc.But we have no help to work with them programatically. So, this package will help you to convert those legacy fonts to Unicode text. To easily encorporate with issues like feeding the LLMs and revert back the llm response to the legacy fonts.\n\n## Available fonts\n- [x] SutonnyMJ\n- [ ] Salma\n- [ ] SolaimanLipi\n- [ ] Nikosh\n\n\n## Features\n```python\nconvert(text:str, font_name:str, to_legacy:bool)->str\navailable_fonts()->list[str]\n```\n## Installation\n\nYou can install the package using pip:\n\n```bash\npip install legacy-font-converter\n```\n\nOr you can install the package from source:\n\n```bash\npip install git+https://github.com/Abdur-Rahim-sheikh/legacy-font-converter.git\n```\n\n## Example usage\n\n```python\nfrom legacy_font_converter import LegacyFontConverter\n```\n\n\n## Reference\n- A big applaus to [True finder studio](https://github.com/truefinderstudio)\n\n"], "modules": [{"name": "legacy_font_converter", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "legacy_font_converter.BestMatch", "xref": {"fqname": "legacy_font_converter.special_trie.BestMatch", "project": null}}, {"name": "legacy_font_converter.LegacyFontConverter", "xref": {"fqname": "legacy_font_converter.legacy_font_converter.LegacyFontConverter", "project": null}}, {"name": "legacy_font_converter.SpecialTrie", "xref": {"fqname": "legacy_font_converter.special_trie.SpecialTrie", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "legacy_font_converter.legacy_font_converter", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "legacy_font_converter.legacy_font_converter.logger", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "legacy_font_converter.legacy_font_converter.legacy_font_converter", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "legacy_font_converter.legacy_font_converter.text", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "legacy_font_converter.legacy_font_converter.sutonnymj", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "legacy_font_converter.legacy_font_converter.converted", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [{"name": "legacy_font_converter.legacy_font_converter.LegacyFontConverter", "bases": [], "methods": [{"name": "legacy_font_converter.legacy_font_converter.LegacyFontConverter.__init__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "legacy_font_converter.legacy_font_converter.LegacyFontConverter.__load_mapper", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "name", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "legacy_font_converter.legacy_font_converter.LegacyFontConverter.convert", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "text", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "font_name", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "to_legacy", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": ["text: string to convert\n\nfont_name: name of the font to convert should be in the available list\n\nto_legacy: if True, convert from font to unicode, else unicode to font"]}, {"name": "legacy_font_converter.legacy_font_converter.LegacyFontConverter.available_fonts", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "list", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.list", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}]}, "documentation": []}], "class_variables": [], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": ["LegacyFontConverter is a class to convert text between legacy fonts and unicode.\nIt uses SpecialTrie to encove the conversion patterns.\nCurrently, it supports the following fonts:\n- sutonnymj\n\nUsage:\nconverter = LegacyFontConverter()\nsutonnymj = \"Avj\u00f8\u00acvn, Av\u00e3yi iwng, Zvi gv\u00d1evev I \u00af\u00cd\u00aax \u2020K Rv\u203abvZyj wdi`vDm `vb Kiyb, Avgxb|\"\nunicode_text = converter.convert(sutonnymj, font_name=\"sutonnymj\")\nprint(unicode_text)\n\nOutput: \"\u0986\u09b2\u09cd\u09b2\u09be\u09b9, \u0986\u09ac\u09cd\u09a6\u09c1\u09b0 \u09b0\u09b9\u09bf\u09ae, \u09a4\u09be\u09b0 \u09ae\u09be-\u09ac\u09be\u09ac\u09be \u0993 \u09b8\u09cd\u09a4\u09cd\u09b0\u09c0 \u0995\u09c7 \u099c\u09be\u09a8\u09cd\u09a8\u09be\u09a4\u09c1\u09b2 \u09ab\u09bf\u09b0\u09a6\u09be\u0989\u09b8 \u09a6\u09be\u09a8 \u0995\u09b0\u09c1\u09a8, \u0986\u09ae\u09c0\u09a8\u0964\"\n\nif you want to convert from unicode to font, set to_legacy=True\nfont_text = converter.convert(unicode_text, font_name=\"sutonnymj\", to_legacy=True)\nprint(font_text)"]}], "exports": []}, {"name": "legacy_font_converter.special_trie", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "legacy_font_converter.special_trie.logger", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "legacy_font_converter.special_trie.file_name", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "legacy_font_converter.special_trie.data", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "legacy_font_converter.special_trie.sutonnymj_to_unicode", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "legacy_font_converter.special_trie.unicode_to_sutonnymj", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "legacy_font_converter.special_trie.original_text", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "legacy_font_converter.special_trie.text", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "legacy_font_converter.special_trie.convert", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "legacy_font_converter.special_trie.convert", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "legacy_font_converter.special_trie.convert_back", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [{"name": "legacy_font_converter.special_trie.Node", "bases": [], "methods": [{"name": "legacy_font_converter.special_trie.Node.__init__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "legacy_font_converter.special_trie.Node.set_leaf", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "value", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "order", "type": {"name": "int", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.int", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "class_variables": [], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": []}, {"name": "legacy_font_converter.special_trie.BestMatch", "bases": [], "methods": [{"name": "legacy_font_converter.special_trie.BestMatch.__init__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "value", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "order", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "legacy_font_converter.special_trie.BestMatch.__str__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "class_variables": [], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": []}, {"name": "legacy_font_converter.special_trie.SpecialTrie", "bases": [], "methods": [{"name": "legacy_font_converter.special_trie.SpecialTrie.__init__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "patterns", "type": {"name": "list", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.list", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}]}, "default": null}, {"name": "values", "type": {"name": "list", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.list", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}]}, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["This special trie matches text replace with the lowest\norder key as the key might have prefix relation.\nSo pass the pattern in a order where earlier pattern will be \nreplaced first.\nargs:\n    patterns: list of unicode patterns in highest to lowest precedence\n    values: list of unicode values for particular pattern\n    note: their length must be same\n    note2: strings should in plain unicode values \n    i.e.:A unicode string for sutonnoymj legacy font \"Avj\u00f8\u00acvn, Av\u00e3yi iwng, Zvi gv\u00d1evev I \u00af\u00cd\u00aax \u2020K Rv\u203abvZyj wdi`vDm `vb Kiyb, Avgxb|\" "]}, {"name": "legacy_font_converter.special_trie.SpecialTrie.convert", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "text", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "legacy_font_converter.special_trie.SpecialTrie.search", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "key", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "legacy_font_converter.special_trie.SpecialTrie.__next", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "char", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "tuple", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.tuple", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "bool", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.bool", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, {"name": "BestMatch", "xref": {"fqname": "legacy_font_converter.special_trie.BestMatch", "project": null}, "params": null}]}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "legacy_font_converter.special_trie.SpecialTrie.__reset_progress", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "legacy_font_converter.special_trie.SpecialTrie.__insert", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "key", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default